Plan
/ Planner LLM call. Per step → {index, actions: ["module.action", ...], group?}.
/ The planner only names which actions are involved; the compiler decides chain order
/ and shape from each action's authored examples.

- set %modules% = %!app.module.list%
- render template "/system/actions/v2/summary.planner.md", write to %actionSummary%
- render template "/system/builder/llm/templates/goalFormat.template", write to %goalForLlm%
- render template "/system/builder/llm/Plan.llm", write to %planPrompt%
- set %messages% = [{"Role":"system", "Content":"%planPrompt%"}, {"Role":"user", "Content":"%goalForLlm%"}]

/ Wrap llm.query + Validate together so the retry surface catches BOTH
/ malformed-JSON (llm.query throws) and structural validation failures
/ (Validate throws step-count-mismatch, etc.). RetryCount=2 is the runtime's
/ job. LlmFixer re-prompts with previousConversation=%plan%.
- call QueryAndValidatePlan, on error call LlmFixer, then retry 2 times

/ Stamp the planner's prompts onto %plan% so the parent's set %trace.plan% = %plan%
/ carries them into the trace for the viewer.
- set %plan.system% = %planPrompt%
- set %plan.user% = %goalForLlm%
- set %plan.usage% = {model: %plan.Model%, promptTokens: %plan.PromptTokens%, cachedTokens: %plan.CachedTokens%, completionTokens: %plan.CompletionTokens%, totalTokens: %plan.TotalTokens%, cost: %plan.Cost%, cached: %plan.Cached%}


QueryAndValidatePlan
- llm.query Messages=%messages%, Schema={description: string, steps: list<{index: int, actions: list<string>, confidence: string, explanation?: string}>}, cache=%!build.cache%, write to %plan%
- call Validate
